Open membership
When [[LiveJournal]] was created, anyone could join any [[community]] [[liberal|she]] wanted. This was called "open membership" and everything was awesome. Now LJ has a "closed community" option, which makes everything suck.

==How to weasel your way into closed communities==
[[Rimjob|Suck as much ass]] of relevant members as possible, to gain:

* Trust
* Respect
* Um...

